data.description: Tucked away in a serene countryside setting, this spacious 3,149 sq ft home offers the perfect blend of rustic charm and modern comfort. With four bedrooms, three full baths, and a double car garage, it provides ample space for family living. The open-concept kitchen, dining, and family room flow seamlessly onto a deck overlooking the wooded forest, while formal dining and living rooms offer additional space for entertaining. Upstairs, a luxurious master suite awaits, complete with a grand ensuite and walk-in closet. A large bonus room provides flexibility for office or playroom use. Downstairs, an unfinished basement offers endless potential for customization, whether as a guest suite or hobby space. Escape to the tranquility of nature while enjoying the comforts of home in this idyllic retreat.
